desc: Our stainless steel travel cutlery set is built for everyday use. These travel utensils are eco-friendly, crafted to last without harming the environment. Say goodbye to takeaway plastic and hello to an easy-to-clean alternative tableware with your own everyday reusable fork, knife, spoon, straw, and straw cleaner.

layout.text: Say goodbye to single use plastic and hello to reusable cutlery
